  "text": "Networking and communication devices such as Ethernet switches and IP routers are found in office buildings, points of presence, colocation and data centers throughout the world. The ubiquity and importance of these devices coupled with their increasing power density [CITATION_1] and associated cooling costs are strong motivations for designing future systems and protocols that are power-aware and power efficient.",
